는 아야 씨를 보고\n아이돌로서 해쳐나갈 꿈과 용기를 받았어요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":218,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":218}],"windowDisplayName":"미오","body":"저희도…… 아야 씨처럼, 꿈과 용기를\n주는 아이돌이 되고싶어요!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":218,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"ViVidCanvas 일동","body":"부탁드립니다!!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":219,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":220,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"히나","body":"호오~ 연습생들이 파스파레 곡을 부른단 말이지……\n그렇구나~……\n그런데 이런 일이 자주 있어?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event135-06-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"스태프","body":"선배 유닛 곡을 후배 유닛이 부르는 일은\n아이돌 업계에서는 자주 있는 일로……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voic